quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Supremely Blessed be He in whose hand is the dominion, and He is All- Powerful over everything;"
  67,2,"the One Who created death and life to test youpl as to which of you is better in conduct, for He is the Almighty, the Oft-Forgiving;"
  67,3,"the One Who created seven heavens in layers: yousg see no discrepancy in the creation of the All-Merciful. So look again: can you see any splits?"
  67,4,"Then look again and again—yoursg sight will return to you bedazzled and exhausted."
  67,5,"And indeed, We have adorned the lowest1heaven with lanterns and made them missiles against the Satans, and We have prepared for them the punishment of the Blaze."
  67,6,"And for those who have denied their Lord is the punishment of Hell, and what a miserable destiny!"
  67,7,"When they are thrown into it, they hear it roaring as it seethes—"
  67,8,"it almost bursts with rage. Every time a crowd is thrown into it, its keepers ask them, “Did no warner come to you?”"
  67,9,"They said1, “Yes, a warner did come to us, but we disbelieved and said, ‘Allah did not bestow anything from on high; it is youpl who are greatly misguided!’”"
  67,10,"And they said, “Had we listened or reasoned, we would not have been among the fellows of the Blaze.”"